    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-ready condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with TMS plates to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The chassis remains rigid, suspended by an untouched factory M-Sport suspension, and power is delivered via a variable M-differential lock. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint correction required, while the interior shows no bolster wear or upholstery delamination. A true purist\u2019s example with a linear 8,000 RPM power band and surgical throttle response.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
