    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly showroom-grade specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, having recently undergone a professional multi-stage paint correction followed by a dual-layer ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule: the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one, and the vehicle has never been smoked in. Every electronic feature, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium surround-sound system, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships. It has just received a comprehensive annual service including all fluid flushes and a multi-point inspection. This sale includes the original window sticker, two master keys, all owner's manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. This is an investment-grade vehicle for a buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46800.0,
